  "panels": [
    {
      "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0},
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "content": "## Restic Backup — Scheduled Nightly via AppRole\n\n**Repo:** `secret/restic/backup` (Vault-stored URL points to MinIO on QNAP `:9000`)\n**Auth:** AppRole `backup` → policy `backup` (read on `secret/restic/backup`, `secret/minio/backup`)\n**Script:** `scripts/backup.sh` — `restic backup` + `restic forget --keep-daily 30 --keep-monthly 12 --prune`\n**Backed-up paths:** `~/repos/integrated-ai-platform/{config,docs,docker/caddy,docker/headscale,scripts}` + Vault data volume",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "Configuration",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 4},
      "id": 100,
      "title": "Snapshot Summary",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {"type": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource", "uid": "${DS_INFINITY}"},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "red", "value": null}, {"color": "green", "value": 1}]},
          "unit": "short",
          "noValue": "(no status file yet)"
        }
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 5},
      "id": 10,
      "options": {"reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"]}, "colorMode": "background", "textMode": "value"},
      "title": "Total Snapshots",
      "type": "stat",
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "type": "json",
          "source": "url",
          "format": "table",
          "url": "http://host.docker.internal:8085/restic-status.json",
          "url_options": {"method": "GET"},
          "columns": [
            {"selector": "snapshot_count", "text": "count", "type": "number"}
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "datasource": {"type": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource", "uid": "${DS_INFINITY}"},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
